org.kocakosm.pitaya.collection

Class ConcurrentHashBag<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • org.kocakosm.pitaya.collection.AbstractBag<E>
        • org.kocakosm.pitaya.collection.ConcurrentHashBag<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of the elements in the bag.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Iterable<E>, Collection<E>, Bag<E>, ConcurrentBag<E>

    public final class ConcurrentHashBag<E>
extends AbstractBag<E>
implements ConcurrentBag<E>, Serializable
    A thread-safe variant of HashBag based on ConcurrentHashMap.
    Author:
    Osman KOCAK
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
